div.p:
427. 1. My telegram number 425, November 1, 3 p.m. Following information
                            from Connor, Tientsin, sent November 2, 11 p.m.: 

“Wu’s Yangtsun position collapsed. Feng’s troops now at Peitang;
                                    all precautions taken against entry soldiers into Tientsin. Feng
                                    warned to observe protocol.”
